items.name: Brutal Legend Wiki
items.title: Brutal Legend Wiki
items.headline: Explore the Age of Metal with Brütal Legend Wiki!
items.desc:
Brütal Legend Wiki is the definitive place for everything Brütal Legend, the action-adventure game created by Tim Schafer and Double Fine, the fine folks who brought you Psychonauts! In addition to in-depth guides and tons of information, BLWikians can join a close community of fans, write blogs, take part in forums, and chat live with other users. Whether you're an old fan of the game, or just curious about it, we invite you to be a part of the most metal wiki on Wikia!

Keep calm and rock on!

items.name: Galaxy Legend Wiki
items.title: Galaxy Legend Wiki
items.headline: Galaxy Legend Do you got what it takes to take on enemies?
items.desc:
This wiki is about Galaxy Legend. Learn all about it!

In the year 2841, a new chapter in the story of humanity is beginning as we expand to the furthest stars in the universe. In a sci-fi landscape of mystery, intrigue, and opportunity, you'll take the reigns as Commander of a galactic outpost vying for power. It won't be easy though, you'll need to marshall all your forces and employ a variety of strategies to repel those who wish to eradicate you. Make no mistake: the threat of Space Pirates, enemy outposts, aliens, and the unknown looms before us. Your legend is waiting to be written, Commander.

items.name: Galaxy Legend Wiki
items.title: Galaxy Legend Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Galaxy Legend Wikia
items.desc:
Until now there was not much to find about Galaxy Legend in the net, this is an attempt to unite the Galaxy Legend community without the borders of single servers. Here we can gather information about the game, exchange tips and tricks and provide a nice start for new players.
This Wikia is far from beeing complete, with the effort of excited users this can be THE place for Galaxy Legend.
